pi4j-components
===============

This artifact is a vendored copy of third-party Apache-2.0-licensed code,
repackaged under ParadigmShift Maven coordinates so it can be consumed from
the ParadigmShift Maven repository (https://maven.paradigmshift.pt) without
depending on third-party hosts that may become unavailable.

